  "title": "Delivery Crew",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Uphold service quality by ensuring timely delivery of goods for customers’ orders</li><li>Receive orders prior to and maintain accuracy of inventory for delivery</li><li>Ensure that all monies are collected in a timely and secure manner.</li><li>Provide exceptional customer service to our clients;</li><li>Take ownership and maintain cleanliness of vehicles assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Qualifications</strong></u></p><ul><li><strong>Class 3 Licence</strong></li><li>Experience as Delivery Crew/ Driver a bonus</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Good driving track records</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Good team player</li><li>Able to work within deadlines and well-organised</li><li>Positive attitude and eager to learn</li><li>Display strong initiative and able to work independently</li><li>Thrive in a fast-paced environment and able to adapt quickly</li></ul>",
